text: Ikwega Catholic Parish (Ancient Catholic Parish found in Mninga District) Mninga is an administrative ward in the Mufindi District of the Iringa Region of Tanzania, East Africa. According to the 2012 census, the ward has a total population of 14,799.Sensa ya 2012, Iringa Region- Mufindi District Council ==References== Category:Wards of Tanzania
title: Mninga
